Red chile salsa.

1 8oz can tomato sauce
1/2 pkg whole tepin chiles (6pcs? confirm)
1 green onion diced small
1/2 fresh tomato diced small
1/2 brown onion diced small
dash oregano
1 clove garlic
salt to taste

Tepins: put in plastic bag and smash until skin has nearly turned to powder.
Put clove of garlic into same plastic bag and smash until nearly all mush.
Mix all ingredients into tomato sauce and stir. All ingredients fresh; no
one is cooking anything here.
